reviews.review_text: Sweet pea!! Thanks for your time and efforts...the sound quality is absolutely top-notch---just exactly perfect.  Patching is excellent where applied.  Both sets are outstanding.  You cannot go wrong with any of these Anchorage shows---but to have them sounding this crisp and clean is a real treat.  These recent clean ups/uploads from Miller and the couple I have found   from Gans are just killin' me! Good stuff! Poke around---they are popping up like mushrooms as of late throughout--especially the early eighties shows, it seems--anyways--Thanks a million.

peggy-o i dont know how many times they played peggy-o in the second set, but it is def a rare occasion.  danks charlie for all your work.
